name: 'The Road to Machu Picchu'
description:
'The Road to Machu Picchu' is artwork by Australian Artist Pedro Matheij and tells a story about a Spiritual Journey that started in The Sacred Valley of Peru and ends at the Ancient Incan Citadel of Machu Picchu.
The artwork has said to contain the energy of the ancient warriors of the past and will bring to the owner great riches and wisdom.
